text: Syed Haider Ali is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Pabna-2. ==Career== Ali was elected to parliament from Pabna-2 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Syed Haider Ali
